page.title: 02Starr Garage, Henham
page.content:
The Starr Garage has been in Henham since 1950. First the Starr Garage
was the Starr Inn and then it became a farm. The Starr Garage opens daily at 8.00am and closes at 7.00pm .The Starr Garage has only one mechanic and the maximum of repairs in a week is 15.The price of a gallon of 4 star petrol is Â£ 2.04 and the Starr Garage sells 1000 gallons a week .In the garage there are two pumps one sells 2 star petrol and the other one sells 4 star petrol. The garage also sells parrafin but not diesel. The garage is run by Mr.P.Meads.
